description.text: NEW CONSTRUCTION - Gorgeous Modern-Style Home! This newly built, modern-style home sits on a spacious corner lot in the highly desirable neighborhood of Westchester. The home offers 4 bedrooms and 2 1/2 bathrooms and 1, 284 square feet of living space. It opens up to an open floor plan on the first floor that pours into the large kitchen. The kitchen features white quartz countertops, custom cabinetry with self-closing drawers, built-in stainless-steel appliances, a stackable washer and dryer, a 5 burner stove, and a large island to entertain guests. A private yard extends around the back of the house, perfect for pets or children to run and play in. Homes have solar panels, tankless water heaters, air conditioning units, and hardwood floors. Nearby access to LAX, shopping centers, the 405 and 105 freeways, Sofi Stadium and Clipper Stadium, and the beach, this home features everything you could be looking for.

description.text: NEW CONSTRUCTION - Gorgeous Modern-Style home sits on a spacious corner lot in the highly desirable neighborhood of Westchester. The main home features 3 bedrooms and 2 1/2 bathrooms with over 2, 148 square feet of living space. The front patio welcomes you to this remarkable open floor plan featuring a spacious living room entry to the left, a large gourmet kitchen to the right, and a 1/2 bath off the living room. Homes have solar panels, tankless water heaters, air conditioning units, and hardwood floors. With nearby access to LAX, shopping centers, the 405 and 105 freeways, Sofi Stadium and Clipper Stadium, and the beach, this home features everything you could be looking for. Luxuriate in unparalleled opulence with this stunning 5-bedroom, 5-bathroom Westchester home boasting a vast lot and luscious, manicured backyard. Step inside and take in the grandeur of the open living and dining areas featuring a breathtaking fireplace and wall-length windows emanating natural light. At the center, the chef's kitchen captivates with its spacious island, quartz countertops, and professional-grade appliances. Unwind on the patio in complete peace and marvel at the lushness of mature avocado and citrus trees in your private, park-like backyard paradise. From the primary suite's balcony enjoy dazzling views of the mountains and DTLA skyline, and enjoy the luxurious ensuite, which rivals most spa accommodations with it's oversized walk-in shower and separate soaking tub that gazes into the dreamy backyard and dual vanities. Three additional bedrooms, two full bathrooms, a flex room (perfect for a den or sixth bedroom) complete the upstairs. Come home to this picturesque, Silicon Beach oasis. Available for move in July 1st, 2023.

This charming West Westchester home is a delightful haven, boasting three bedrooms and two bathrooms, providing ample space for comfort and privacy. Step inside and be greeted by the warmth of natural light that floods through large windows, creating an inviting and cozy ambiance. The hardwood floors add a touch of elegance, complementing the modern design and enhancing the overall aesthetic appeal. The kitchen and bathrooms have been tastefully remodeled, combining functionality with style. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring sleek countertops, Bosch appliances, and ample storage space. The bathrooms have received a stunning makeover, with modern fixtures, elegant tiling, and a contemporary design. Step outside into the elegant backyard to sip your morning coffee or host a lively barbecue with friends and family, this outdoor space is perfect for creating lasting memories. This incredible home also comes with a new washer and dryer, and the two-car garage offers plenty of space for your vehicles and additional storage needs. It's a sanctuary of comfort, style, and modern living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home sweet home. Fireplace is for effect only and will not be used for wood or gas fires.

Inside, you will be greeted by a spacious living room with oak hardwood floors and a fireplace. An entertainers grand room with a bar opens to the rear yard and sparkling pool. Enjoy an abundance of natural sunlight in this beautiful home with large windows beaming in from almost every direction. The chef's kitchen has been remodeled with stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops and a bonus study area. The oversized sunroom offers a flexible space for a pool room, yoga or art center. The primary bedroom has a built-in closet, extra storage and an ensuite bath with a sunken tub overlooking a Zen garden. The two other bedrooms are generously sized with hardwood floors and closets. Park-like rear yard with pool perfect for warm summer nights. Two-car garage, carport and driveway parking for multiple cars. Don't miss out on this stunning opportunity!

description.text: Welcome to ST Living @ Ramsgate, the perfect place to call home! Our stunning townhomes offer an unparalleled living experience that you won't find anywhere else. Enjoy breathtaking views of the city skyline from your very own rooftop sky deck, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing after a long day. Inside, you'll find spacious living areas with stylish flooring and two-tone cabinetry that complement the sleek stainless steel appliances and elegant quartz countertops. Stay comfortable year-round with mobile-friendly thermostats, central A/C and heat, and the convenience of an in-unit washer and dryer. Plus, never worry about finding a parking spot with our reserved parking, ensuring you always have a spot to come home to. Located in Westchester, an up-and-coming neighborhood in West LA, our townhomes are in close proximity to LAX, Loyola Marymount University, and the highly-acclaimed Enriched Sciences Magnet School, making it the perfect spot for families, students, and working professionals alike. We understand that pets are family too, which is why our townhomes are both dog- and cat-friendly. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to elevate your lifestyle. Contact us today to schedule a tour and discover what makes our community so special.
